fields.name: Include
fields.description:
Type of files, which need to be included in the logs
This will contain the type of logs (Default/DefaultWithDumps/None/All/DefaultWithArchived)
or a comma separated list of log types that are required

fields.name: MaximumTimeStamp
fields.description: Start of the timespan of the log collection

fields.name: MinimumTimeStamp
fields.description: MinimumTimeStamp from where logs need to be collected
